{"tid":2016021,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[做訪問][急]有冇人係女權/婦女機構做野? 得閑嘅絲巴都可以幫手","createTime":"2020-05-14T05:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T06:50:16.000Z","uid":231351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9904e72a101bc5ae20c133088f770080db9878ec","tid":2016021,"uid":231351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"下星期一要交紀錄片嘅劇本，由於肺炎關係，份功課淨係交劇本，唔洗拍片，亦唔洗面對面訪談。所以可以做網上訪問。<br />\n<br />\n紀錄片嘅主題係關於《女權?自助餐》時長約9分鐘。目的是為大眾釐清女權的定義並令大家反思「女權自助餐」在香港的情況。<br />\n<br />\n所以想請相關人士做訪問，由於我遲開始做，就算send 左 e mail 問2間機構，我諗佢地都冇咁快應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以走偏門方法啦。想係度睇下有冇係女權機構做嘅人，而對女權嘅議題熟悉嘅人幫手做訪問。<br />\n<br />\n另外，誠意邀請2絲2巴做另一個訪問亦關於女權嘅。<br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd48827dd978cd8f65e39ac8066318890437cc61","tid":2016021,"uid":231351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"我知我衰女遲開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4941642f2c3d6fb407aa276378aac377a8c526a4","tid":2016021,"uid":231351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"有意可留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9695a75bcc8991aba77aed14d8e929f7372625","tid":2016021,"uid":297436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"今日星期幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下星期一交依家先搵<img src=\"/ass